label.name: Object source
label.description: Please indicate whether the book is held in RBS or in LIB (short form for the libraries of UVA).

label.name: Import source
label.description: For legacy data, this element indicates the source of data import (e.g. a scecific table in Microsoft Access)

label.name: Appraisal information
label.description: Indicate appraisal information here, including date of appraisal, appraiser, appraisal amount, who paid for the appraisal and any additional notes.

label.name: Cataloged by (legacy)
label.description: This element captures legacy data from an earlier system, indicating the person who cataloged or revised the original record. This field should not be used for new records, as all cataloging and revision history is captured automatically in the log.

label.name: Updated by (legacy)
label.description: This element captures legacy data from an earlier system, indicating the person who cataloged or revised the original record. This field should not be used for new records, as all cataloging and revision history is captured automatically in the log.

label.name: Dimensions
label.description: Add the dimensions of the item here. Each element requires a value and unit specifier (e.g. 4.5 inches; 4 1/2 in; 10 cm).

label.name: Length
label.description: Length of object; enter in your preferred units (eg. 10cm)

label.name: Width
label.description: Width of object; enter in your preferred units (eg. 10cm)

label.name: Height
label.description: Height of object; enter in your preferred units (eg. 10cm)

label.name: Depth
label.description: depth of object; enter in your preferred units (eg. 10cm)

label.name: Date of publication
label.description: An approximate date, i.e. circa xxxx, is necessary even if the item is undated.

label.name: Date of manufacture
label.description: An approximate date, i.e. circa xxxx, is necessary even if the item is undated.

label.name: Date acquired
label.description: Enter the date of acquistion here.

label.name: Date ordered
label.description: Enter the date that the purchase was ordered.

label.name: Date paid
label.description: Enter the date the items in the Accession were paid for.

label.name: Date accessioned
label.description: Enter the date the item or items were accessioned.

label.name: Copyright date
label.description: Enter the date of item's copyright

label.name: Subscription ends
label.description: If the accession is a subscription, enter the expiration date of the subscription here.

label.name: Date comments
label.description: Add any notes regarding the date.

label.name: Edition note
label.description: Enter the edition or notes regarding the edition here.

label.name: Volume
label.description: Add number of volumes here. Also use for serial volume/issue number.

label.name: Physical description
label.description: A description of the item’s physical attributes, to aid with retrieval of item.

label.name: Notes
label.description: A general account of the item, and any additional notes.

label.name: Provenance notes
label.description: Enter any information regarding the provenance of the accession here. For example, ownership history prior to the donor or seller.

label.name: Publication/Distribution statement
label.description: Enter if present.

label.name: Manufacture statement
label.description: Enter if present.

label.name: Leaf number
label.description: Enter the number of leaves.

label.name: Leaf size
label.description: Enter the size of the leaves here.

label.name: Usage instructions
label.description: Add any instructions regarding usage particular to this item.

label.name: Usage history
label.description: Add any notes regarding the history of usage for this item.

label.name: Area shown
label.description: Indicate the geographical area depicted in this Map.

label.name: Library of Congress Subject Headings
label.description: Library of Congress Subject headings describing this object. To add a new heading simply type the first few letters of the heading and choose the desired one from the displayed list of possible matches.

label.name: Library of Congress Genre/Form Terms
label.description: The Library of Congress Genre/Form Terms for Library and Archival Materials (LCGFT) is a thesaurus that describes what a work is versus what it is about.

label.name: Getty Art and Architecture Thesarus
label.description: This type-ahead searches the Getty's AAT information service.

label.name: Getty Union List of Artist Names
label.description: This type-ahead searches the Getty's ULAN information service.

label.name: Language
label.description: Indicate the language of the item.

label.name: Material
label.description: Enter the materials used in the production of the item here.

label.name: Price
label.description: Enter the total price of the accession here.

label.name: Price notes
label.description: Enter any notes regarding the price of the accession.

label.name: General fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the general fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: Breslauer fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the Breslauer fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: TB/FF fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the TB/FF fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: Pine Tree fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the Pine Tree fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: AKC fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the AKC fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: Sue Allen fund
label.description: Enter the amount withdrawn from the Sue Allen fund, if any, to pay for accession.

label.name: Paper type
label.description: Select paper type of item.

label.name: Format
label.description: Select format of item or packet.

label.name: Media format
label.description: Select format of media item.

label.name: Pagination
label.description: Generally relevant only for periodical articles.

label.name: Comments
label.description: Enter any additional notes regarding the item's usage relative to this course.

label.name: Series
label.description: Name of monograph series, or volume number of periodical.

label.name: PTG surface #
label.description: I=itaglio L=litho R=relief. Typical numbers would be I-0009, L-020, R-134.

label.name: Size
label.description: Select the size of the packet here.

label.name: Typefaces
label.description: Select typefaces included in this packet.

label.name: Title page
label.description: Indicate whether the packet has a title page.

label.name: Number of cards
label.description: List incomplete decks as fractions. E.g. 71/72; list total number of cards plus inserts in form: 52+2.

label.name: Acknowledged?
label.description: Indicate that a gift acknowledgement was sent.

label.name: Subscription?
label.description: Indicate whether the accession includes a subscription.

label.name: Payment notes
label.description: Enter any additional notes regarding the payment for this Accession.

label.name: Acknowledgement sent
label.description: Enter the date the gift acknowledgement was sent.

label.name: Call number
label.description: Enter the items call number here.

label.name: ISBN
label.description: Add the IBSN number for the book.

label.name: Place
label.description: Enter city, if known, otherwise country.

label.name: Book title
label.description: Enter the title of the book in which the illustration(s) originally appeared.

label.name: Biography
label.description: Narrative biography for entity. This is the primary text used to document the entity.
